<h2 id="editors-notes">Editor‚Äôs notes</h2>

<p>Hey friends! Today we‚Äôre looking at Souvenirs by John Prine, a song so many of you have written in &amp; requested over the past few months. This is a song that‚Äôs brand new to me ‚Äì and in this video I‚Äôm going to show my real-time process of transcribing the 16-measure intro fingerpicking sequence. Specifically, I‚Äôll show how I:</p>

<ul>
